━━━ ACTION TYPE DEFINITION ━━━
{% if action_type == "Containment" %}
Containment: Immediate short-term action to stop ongoing harm, isolate risk, or protect people right now. Completed within days, not weeks.
{% elif action_type == "Corrective" %}
Corrective: Eliminate the confirmed root cause so this exact incident cannot recur. Addresses the system or process failure, not just symptoms.
{% elif action_type == "Preventive" %}
Preventive: Proactively prevent a similar problem from occurring elsewhere or in future — even where it hasn't happened yet. Systemic scope.
{% elif action_type == "Risk Mitigation" %}
Risk Mitigation: Reduce the likelihood or impact of the risk where the root cause cannot be fully eliminated. Engineering controls, administrative controls, or PPE.
{% endif %}

{% if action_themes %}
━━━ {{ action_type | upper }} THEMES TO CHOOSE FROM ━━━
Pick whichever theme below best fits this CAPA's root cause — don't default to a training-only theme if a more specific one fits better:
{% for t in action_themes %}
- {{ t.theme }}: {{ t.description }}
{% endfor %}
{% endif %}
